            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Maximianus hic in pac<surplus>a</surplus>e <lb n="2"/>iacet qui <expan><ex>vi</ex><abbr>xit</abbr></expan> annos LXV <lb n="3"/>et menses IIII et dies XX <lb n="4"/>Memoriosus et Prudens <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> sui titiulum fecerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung einer Vase mit flankierenden Tauben.</p>
            </div>
